118
00:09:42,125 --> 00:09:43,455
Hebatnya.

119
00:09:43,541 --> 00:09:46,631
Itu memang hebat. Besar betul benda itu.

120
00:09:46,708 --> 00:09:48,578
- Ya, betul.
- Besar, bukan?

121
00:09:48,666 --> 00:09:50,326
Sangat besar. Hei.

122
00:10:01,458 --> 00:10:03,128
Hei, Sedge, nak ikut?

123
00:10:09,791 --> 00:10:10,631
Ya.

124
00:10:12,291 --> 00:10:13,961
Ya, saya datang.

125
00:10:14,041 --> 00:10:17,461
Tengok cara ia ambil nafas? Menakjubkan.

126
00:10:17,541 --> 00:10:21,711
Itu tiada di Bumi. Hebat betul.

127
00:10:22,583 --> 00:10:24,213
Ya, saya tahu.

128
